structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
ISSUANCE OF BONDS AND CONTROL OF FUNDS

law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 280, sec. 30, effective July 15, 1996; amended ch. 195, sec. 31, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 7. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1852.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Advertisement and election to refund or pay county bonds issued for railroad purposes.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/96). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 280 prevails over its amendment in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 195.
